                              <div className="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-2xl p-5 text-left border border-gray-700/50 backdrop-blur-sm"> <div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3 pb-3 border-b border-gray-700/50"> <User className="text-gray-500" size={16}/> <span className="font-bold text-white">{selectedOrder.clientName}</span> </div> <div className="flex items-start gap-3"> <MapPin className="text-gray-500 mt-0.5" size={16}/> <span className="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-snug">{selectedOrder.address}</span> </div> </div>
                          </div>

                          <div className="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-5 text-left border border-gray-700 shadow-lg animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
                              <h4 className="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"> <Gift size={16} className="text-pink-400"/> 填寫回饋．領取好禮 </h4>
                              <p className="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed"> 感謝您的支持！完成以下兩項任務，我們將致贈 <span className="text-yellow-400 font-bold">7-11 City Cafe 兌換券兩張</span> 以表謝意。 </p>
                              <div className="space-y-3">
                                  <a href="https://forms.gle/Lv2pyTuwyxgSACr47" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" className="flex items-center justify-between bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600 p-3 rounded-xl transition group"> <span className="text-sm font-bold text-gray-200 flex items-center gap-2"> <Clipboard size={16} className="text-blue-400"/> 填寫滿意度問卷 </span> <ArrowRight size={16} className="text-gray-500 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition"/> </a>
                                  <a href="https://reurl.cc/ZNdR0V" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" className="flex items-center justify-between bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600 p-3 rounded-xl transition group"> <span className="text-sm font-bold text-gray-200 flex items-center gap-2"> <Star size={16} className="text-yellow-400"/> 給予 Google 評論 </span> <ArrowRight size={16} className="text-gray-500 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition"/> </a>
                              </div>
                          </div>

